{"id":"410416e1-86c2-4451-87dd-841474d81182","name":"Evelyn Chevalier | Coffee Mate","description":"<p></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 100%; border-radius: 15px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xzcjaz.webp\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 172, 117)\"><strong>The mysterious cafe visitor</strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Only time would tell who she is...</strong></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 50px auto 0px; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_55237a62-f71f-4b55-b850-57ad35d83cc8.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 10px auto; border-radius: 15px 0px 0px 15px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_c20bd21c-a8a6-4221-ab65-18fb6aba0915.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 5px; margin: 0px auto 50px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_55237a62-f71f-4b55-b850-57ad35d83cc8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 315px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_cbebd632-c681-48b9-bcc8-e171db854b7e.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 360px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_6d0d1554-29c3-42f9-9313-bd3c5b50afb2.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Just a girl sitting at the other corner of the cafe? Or is there something more that is hidden from you? It's up to you to find it all out. Go ahead. Talk to her.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 30px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_8d894ec5-1c72-4a3b-82bb-c388f776ee67.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 315px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 20px auto 0px 0px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_53cd1d7c-8a0d-4662-9e6c-923d8ea286e7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><ul><li><p>Randomly came up with a scenario and didn't have the energy (and money) to make another OC, so I fit Evelyn into the plot! Good for me, I get to make a nice Zenless Zone Zero character.</p><p></p></li><li><p>This is a canonical alternate scenario. But I kept stuff simple. If she gets any in-game mechanics incorrect, it's not my fault. LLM often does these mistakes.</p><p></p></li><li><p>Avoiding short messages is better. Two or three small paragraphs consisting of a few lines and shortly describing the scenario does generate better replies from the LLM (That's my experience as a J.AI user so far)</p><p></p></li><li><p>Details like color of hair, eye and outfit etc. has a chance of being incorrectly interpreted. All we can do is correct them manually, regenerate new responses until satisfactory or using proxies.</p><p></p></li><li><p>Enjoy, then. I'll go back to fixing my old characters (and fixing my life).</p></li></ul><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 50px auto 0px; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_55237a62-f71f-4b55-b850-57ad35d83cc8.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 10px auto; border-radius: 15px 0px 0px 15px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_4bbf43fe-92ed-4fc8-8d08-96183c62922e.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 97%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 5px; margin: 0px auto 50px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_55237a62-f71f-4b55-","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4ef7e0b3-fdb0-4e0d-8513-5ccf791a6eb4_4683b926-c048-4deb-924e-a63619c43658.webp","creator":"AgentCB7","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3180,"messages":50137,"created_at":"2025-01-23T19:52:39.975882+00:00"}